{"tid":607740,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費Sir涉23億鎊有組織逃稅案","createTime":"2018-03-27T14:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T09:50:04.000Z","uid":20634,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3689236b9a0a262c60f1eb97e864f7928d90a26f","tid":607740,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Wx6tw4pFrpoXHRStRrmFkcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=eea98e6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】西班牙逃稅風波蔓延到英格蘭，牽涉多名球壇中人，包括前曼聯領隊費格遜。<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》周一報道，英國稅務海關總署最近正在調查一宗逃稅案，涉案人士利用政府對電影業嘅稅項優惠，假借投資之名，合共逃避了高達23億鎊稅項，而且是一個涉及780人的有組織逃稅計劃。<br />\n<br />\n780人當中，有不少是球壇中人，包括前曼聯領隊費格遜（Sir Alex Ferguson）、前英格蘭主帥荷杜、艾歷臣，以及紐卡素翼鋒蘇蘭奴、伯明翰左翼拿沙迪斯等多名前英超球員。英國退役球員福利組織Xpro證實，有多名前球員涉事，但他們辯稱不知道今次投資其實是逃稅。<br />\n<br />\n一經定罪，稅務海關總署將會向涉案人士收取懲罰性稅收，即應付稅項的20倍，屆時將令不少人無力清還而申請破產。"},{"pid":"275760996c77ff597cc8497ed05d1d966d97e6bc","tid":607740,"uid":20634,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/221210_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F221210_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=09b58de8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d838d7d8ef260e097abf7154753347d887cfe69c","tid":607740,"uid":20634,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">費格遜，全能到仆街</span></span>"},{"pid":"b2b3a2ca32a1423cff13ad0c98471a4f185a2903","tid":607740,"uid":20634,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39362cbda375036224dcac280d65ea8312d6cdd8","tid":607740,"uid":83648,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"名師出高徒"},{"pid":"9792b3d0f98dfe018cdc7fe701ad5c0dcd12d0ca","tid":607740,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"拿拿臨拉鳩佢啦"},{"pid":"e699a1fe13f246170b4767018df34517455d221b","tid":607740,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"23億鎊x20<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n賣菊花都唔撚掂"},{"pid":"4dfb436c3571f9daa533aa085074c147e2b21e0e","tid":607740,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"監獄聯名帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d23603f11316a3ab7cbeb0b40f3c18a07ecf625","tid":607740,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"人魔合一！"},{"pid":"ae509b3157a8912a15980ad810becdc9d94946b2","tid":607740,"uid":65298,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"今次班人冇得話西班牙政府好等錢駛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a773e2440a3672f83a85033ae314787d299f67c","tid":607740,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e428ff4a9095fc0cdc15b014a4889bdda00c44a9","tid":607740,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"食住花生睇好戲"},{"pid":"1efe458f1db543f936c0c3d9c9db42f334608be9","tid":607740,"uid":143190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"英國政府好等錢駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95247f537c9402da1621d334b604e00831705142","tid":607740,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":